remy|title=Koronavirus: 32 p\u0159\u00edpad\u016f, kontroly na hranic\u00edch i omezen\u00ed v domovech senior\u016f|website=idnes.cz|access-date=2020-03-08}}</ref>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" rowspan=2 style=\"text-align:center;\" | '''28'''\n| 8 March 2020\n| {{Partial failure|Confirmed}}\n| {{Success|Travel-related}}\n| {{flag|Italy}}, [[Val Gardena]]\n| [[Prague]]\n| [[Prague]]\n| {{Success|Home isolation}}\n| Female\n| {{n/a}}\n| {{flag|CZE}}\n|- class=\"expand-child\"\n| colspan=\"10\" | A married couple (#27, #28) who had been skiing in Val Gardena resort in Italy with a group of people who were tested posively in previous days.<ref name=\"case27-32.idnes\"/>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" rowspan=2 style=\"text-align:center;\" | '''29'''\n| 8 March 2020\n| {{Partial failure|Confirmed}}\n| {{Success|Travel-related}}\n| {{flag|Italy}}, [[Auronzo di Cadore]]\n| [[Litom\u011b\u0159ice]]\n| [[\u00dast\u00ed nad Labem Region]]\n| {{Success|Home isolation}}\n| Female\n| {{n/a}}\n| {{flag|CZE}}\n|- class=\"expand-child\"\n| colspan=\"10\" | Women (case #29, #30) from a group that visited Auronzo di Cadore ski resort in Italy.<ref name=\"cases29-30-twitter\">{{cite web|url=https://twitter.com/adamvojtechano/status/1236675323149930496|title=Twitter update from Minister of Health|website=twitter.com|access-date=2020-03-08}}</ref>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" rowspan=2 style=\"text-align:center;\" | '''30'''\n| 8 March 2020\n| {{Partial failure|Confirmed}}\n| {{Success|Travel-related}}\n| {{flag|Italy}}, [[Auronzo di Cadore]]\n| [[Litom\u011b\u0159ice]]\n| [[\u00dast\u00ed nad Labem Region]]\n| {{Success|Home isolation}}\n| Female\n| {{n/a}}\n| {{flag|CZE}}\n|- class=\"expand-child\"\n| colspan=\"10\" | Women (case #29, #30) from a group that visited Auronzo di Cadore ski resort in Italy.<ref name=\"cases29-30-twitter\"/>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" rowspan=2 style=\"text-align:center;\" | '''31'''\n| 8 March 2020\n| {{Partial failure|Confirmed}}\n| {{Partial failure|Person-to-person spread}}\n| {{fla